	<h1 class="title">如果你喜欢Gucci的设计，不妨了解一下这个“鱼”先生</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/75588/small/75588.jpg?1431919455" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张金晶 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-07 12:57:06 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/23384/medium/23384.jpg?1457279004" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="23384" data-title="《如果你喜欢Gucci的设计，不妨了解一下这个“鱼”先生》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/23384/medium/23384.jpg?1457279004" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/23384.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
